Adobe Analytics Audit

Summary

Below is a summary of what we found when checking the ageo1xxpnwsdi2020prod report suite looking at data from 2021-10-28 to 2021-12-26.

Note: The raw data for everything that follows is available in this Google Sheet.

When it comes to traffic sources:

  • There were 74 unique values for the campaign variable (tracking code).
  • The campaign variable (tracking code) has 5 classifications configured.
  • Of those, 5 of the classifications are being populated with values.

Of the 6 marketing channels that recorded visits:

  • 1 channels each account for less than 1% of total visits to the site.
  • Internal appears as a marketing channel accounting for 1.1% of traffic, which is somewhat concerning.
